@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cejnor(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 - (v0 + 0.18 + tmp + 0.00)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.00)) + wp.abs(tmp))
    v2 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.64 - v1 + 0.22) + (v1 + 0.26 / tmp + 0.89)))
    v0 = 0.31
    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = (tmp + wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.27)))
    data[tid] = v0
